The paper discusses the use of natural language processing, information retrieval, and machine learning in predicting question deletion in Community Question Answering (CQA) forums. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories of arXiv CS. Among these, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category as the paper focuses on information retrieval techniques for predicting question deletion.
